    <h2>Restart all servers</h2>
    <pre class='prettyprint lang-sh'>cap production deploy:<b>restart</b></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="span6">
    <h2>Deploy to a specific server</h2>
    <pre class='prettyprint lang-sh'>cap production deploy <b>HOSTS</b>=target_server</pre>
  </div>

  <div class="span6">
    <h2>Switch to maintenance</h2>
    <pre class='prettyprint lang-sh'>cap production deploy:<b>web:disable</b></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="span6">
    <h2>Multiple environments</h2>
    <pre class='prettyprint lang-sh'>cap <b>staging</b> deploy</pre>
  </div>

